data.description: Beautiful custom Arthur Rutenberg Home built in the gated neighborhood of the Plantation at College Point.  This home was built with detail and quality.  There are 3 bedrooms,  2.5 bathrooms, office, large bonus room on the second level and gorgeous pool with hot tub.  The open floor plan gives plenty of room for large gatherings but also gives privacy with split bedrooms.  The gourmet kitchen offers giant island, granite countertops, coffee station, gas range, large pantry and stainless steel appliances. The master suite has spacious bedroom, bathroom, walk in closet and huge walk in shower.  Upstairs has bonus room and half bathroom.  The backyard is a water lovers dream.
